{"tid":1397603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧小平外甥女920萬沽映灣園   低沽價11%","createTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:40:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5e5fa33316bf5410a1829cd391c32813219863","tid":1397603,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"鄧小平外甥女920萬沽映灣園   低沽價11%<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月24日<br />\n<br />\n反修例遊行上周到中聯辦門外示威，引發中央負面情緒，已故國家領導人鄧小平外甥女栗小兵，再次低價沽貨離場。<br />\n<br />\n土地注冊處資料顯示，東涌映灣園5座低層H室，實用面積956方呎，三房套間隔，上月以920萬元沽出，呎價9623元，呎價跌穿1萬元，更較恒生銀行估價1040萬元，低出11%。原業主為栗小兵，她於2016年，以750萬元購入，持貨約3年半，帳面獲利170萬元，升值幅度23%。<br />\n<br />\n栗小兵近年睇淡本港住宅物業前景，連環沽出物業，例如上月以5,866萬元，沽出與丈夫俞一平持有的西半山蔚然單位，2017年以約2255萬元沽出，東涌海珀名邸一幢洋房，扣除厘印費及佣金等後，實際損手料約110萬元。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190724/59858782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59858782&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=9aeb2a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59858782&h=8da1e03d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190724/59858782</a>"},{"pid":"4445aafcaf9940f1cb31acc51db6951a5d2cf3ac","tid":1397603,"uid":72058,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43a2ce7e5e4c97bceca2fb70864c19e54f9e496","tid":1397603,"uid":243380,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"佢知黎緊會暴跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真焦土is coming to town<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4afb82d9e386477cd9a1813ac6b4121e82cbaf2","tid":1397603,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p